Package com.sciencesakura.dbsetup.csv

Class Import

java.lang.Object
com.sciencesakura.dbsetup.csv.Import
All Implemented Interfaces:
Operation
public class Import
extends Object
implements Operation
An operation which imports a CSV file into a table.

Usage: 


 // `testdata.csv` must be in classpath.
 Operation operation = csv("testdata.csv").into("tablename").build();
 DbSetup dbSetup = new DbSetup(destination, operation);
 dbSetup.launch();

This operation just uses the Insert operation internal, does not 'upsert'.
